Big Deal Alerts:
——————————————————————————————————————————
setup search -> big deal alert

sometimes, you will want to alert the biggest players about huge opportunities. 
	EX: anytime an opportunity of $1,000,000 is in place and the probability hits 50%, alert folks higher up in the food chain

this alert will be in the form of an email thats sent out autoamtically when the money and probability amount conditions are met
